{"tid":908891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"富二代同志付錢買女友 （周顯）","createTime":"2018-11-20T02:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T09:54:14.000Z","uid":214127,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f5b69b1f7e8ee9c985294a64098150815a8228","tid":908891,"uid":214127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:37:27.000Z","msg":"據說，男同性戀的數目，大約是男人總數的10%，憑我的個人觀察，10%也許比較誇大，但2%至5%總是有的。照這個比率，很肯定地，很多富豪家族的二代，都是屬於這族群。<br />\n<br />\n然而，就算在這個思想開放的年代，仍然有不少人對同性戀懷有偏見，同樣地，也有不少同性戀者有自卑感，就我所見的，資深大律師有同志，立法會議員有同志，但都是出了櫃，公開承認，然而在富豪家族的二代，卻從來沒有見過坦承出櫃的。<br />\n<br />\n有一個地產富二代，今年四十零歲，他有一個富二代女友，拍了幾年拖，沒有下下，後來女友改嫁了。據說，兩人拍拖幾年，只是嘴過兩次咋，陰功！老實講，咁嘥料，好多人都好想上佢條女架！<br />\n<br />\n這些富二代為了掩飾身分，找影子女友是常事。我有一個朋友，有一個女友，是某同志富二代的前度，她對我的朋友說﹕「嗚嗚嗚，阿邊個，搞基都唔搞我呀！」後來這位富二代同志想通了，花錢去買女友，仲生埋仔添，當然，代價非常昂貴，億億聲啦。<br />\n<br />\n也有出手比較低的，有位地產富二代同志，其明星女友的薪水是五百萬元月薪，有女仔聽到後，都說﹕「我都好想做呢份工呀！」我說﹕「不過做呢份工，不准溝仔架喎。」但無論如何，這都是一份筍工，相信五百萬元還有掩口費的作用&hellip;&hellip;不過，在這個世界上，又邊度有秘密吖？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/realtime/article/20181120/2_638616_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181120%2F2_638616_0&d=1evtzUfH0shwkrE1NDTs3Izu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=49f8d2e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181120%2F2_638616_0&h=5d980dfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/realtime/article/20181120/2_638616_0</a><br />\n<br />\n講邊個呢？"},{"pid":"e6346429cc6c99be277ea12704ff0d9774b7291b","tid":908891,"uid":16408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:39:46.000Z","msg":"pccw<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8c082f0d137581d2c0f6604b3cfc7bed26c49f","tid":908891,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:40:49.000Z","msg":"誠仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a46d5ea8a17b975213cbc31e60936a8b60dd918","tid":908891,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:42:57.000Z","msg":"vodafone"},{"pid":"23f60f1237ce8ffd59c9ee14121f5181dee26aa3","tid":908891,"uid":214127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:49:15.000Z","msg":"篇野講緊有兩個人<br />\n生左仔就係誠仔，另一個呢？"},{"pid":"6cf158f629753bf105d8d054ef3c7d95297360d2","tid":908891,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23f60f1237ce8ffd59c9ee14121f5181dee26aa3","tid":908891,"uid":214127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:49:15.000Z","msg":"篇野講緊有兩個人<br />\n生左仔就係誠仔，另一個呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:51:02.000Z","msg":"數字叔個大仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb1f0419680d6143a9248aaa5d5a8274c7dbae5","tid":908891,"uid":55327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}